				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The information that was "leaked" was a post from the the <span style="font-weight: bold">private</span> Development boards/Beta Test boards owned by SOE. All that information unless released by SOE was bound and is still bound by an NDA.
<br />

<br />
The line requesting feedback was feedback from the testers at the time and the other SOE staff working on the project.
<br />

<br />
The proposed changes may never make it into the game, they may make it into the game.
<br />

<br />
Now let me be really clear here, any leaked information will be removed. The posters IP will be passed onto SOE. The person leaking the information stands a real chance of loosing their EQ account.
<br />

<br />
Posts like this if continued will undermine the trust between SOE and its testers and SOE may decide to shut down the Beta Test boards, that option has been discussed if these leaks continue.
<br />

<br />
I should not need to tell you this folks.
<br />

<br />
Final point of thought, anyone who has been using this site pre Luclin will know the entire site was actually shut down because this kind of information was released before. It would be very easy for SOE to request the same again if they thought I was responsible for breaking my personal NDA with them.
<br />

<br />
Think before you post.<br />_________________<br />- Ronaldor Vladimir
