Very well said.  I have to admit I have seen this as the main problem with SoE's player communication for several years.
<br />

<br />
I believe that the mage community was and is more so a subject of this sort of "some players are more equal then others" bullshit since pratically from the begining.  I can only think this was the case because the class itself was subjected to more balance issues.
<br />

